caption:
MORE COWBELL!!! Yup, it’s sunglasses celebrating 50 years of Saturday Night Live! What are your favorite sketches or characters? We already know your favorite cast members: whoever was on when you were in high school.

These 3 limited-edition shades have everything. Roseanne Roseannadanna. Bears Superfans. Mary Katherine Gallagher. The Californians. Featuring snazzy custom packaging, they might be an even better gift than a D*ck in a Box.

Snag ‘em fast! When these sunnies are gone, we’ll have to tell you we sold out & be a total Debbie Downer.
